        </div>

        <input type="number" class="custom-amount" placeholder="Enter custom amount (¬£)" min="1"
          id="custom-amount-input" onchange="selectCustomAmount()" />

        <div id="paypal-donate-button-container"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cause-info">
      <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: #333; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
        <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i>
        About This Cause
      </h2>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <div style="font-size: 4rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">üéì</div>
        <h3 style="color: #333; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Education Changes Lives</h3>
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6;">
          We believe that education is the foundation of progress. Our mission is to
